31#ifndef __LIBELF_AR_H_
32#define __LIBELF_AR_H_
33
34/*
35 * Prototypes and declarations needed by libelf's ar(1) archive
36 * handling code.
37 */
38
39#include <ar.h>
40
41#define LIBELF_AR_BSD_EXTENDED_NAME_PREFIX "#1/"
42#define LIBELF_AR_BSD_SYMTAB_NAME "__.SYMDEF"
43#define LIBELF_AR_BSD_EXTENDED_NAME_PREFIX_SIZE \
44 (sizeof(LIBELF_AR_BSD_EXTENDED_NAME_PREFIX) - 1)
45
46#define IS_EXTENDED_BSD_NAME(NAME) \
47 (strncmp((const char *) (NAME), \
48 LIBELF_AR_BSD_EXTENDED_NAME_PREFIX, \
49 LIBELF_AR_BSD_EXTENDED_NAME_PREFIX_SIZE) == 0)
50
51
52unsigned char *_libelf_ar_get_string(const char *_buf, size_t _sz,
53 unsigned int _rawname, int _svr4names);
54char *_libelf_ar_get_raw_name(const struct ar_hdr *_arh);
55char *_libelf_ar_get_translated_name(const struct ar_hdr *_arh, Elf *_ar);
56int _libelf_ar_get_number(const char *_buf, size_t _sz,
57 unsigned int _base, size_t *_ret);
58
59#endif /* __LIBELF_AR_H_ */
